# Installation of GHC 7.10.2

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution  
cd $HOME/Downloads  

wget https://www.haskell.org/ghc/dist/7.10.2/ghc-7.10.2-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2   
tar xvfj ghc-7.10.2-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2  

cd ghc-7.10.2  

# install to  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-7.10.2  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-7.10.2  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd $HOME/Downloads  
rm -rfv ghc-7.10.2*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
switchghc 7.10.2 
~~~